    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "私が『恋のタクト』にメインキャストとして出演！？\nあの大人気恋愛小説の実写ドラマ化ですよね！？",
      "startTime": 5.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、その認識で間違いない\nそれにゴールデンタイムの二時間枠だぞ",
      "startTime": 12.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "前の雑誌のインタビューで『恋のタクト』について熱く\n語っていただろう。それが先方の目に留まったみたいだ",
      "startTime": 18.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはなんだか恥ずかしいですね……\nあの時、結構我を忘れて語っていた気がするので……",
      "startTime": 27.3272552808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないさ\nそれに沙季からも面白い作品だって聞いたぞ\n心情描写が豊かな恋愛小説……なんだよな？",
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　お話自体は王道のラブストーリーなのに\n一つ一つの感情や情景の描写がほんっとうに素敵で……",
      "startTime": 46.7266610783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "主人公のユイナは恋愛に興味なんてなかったんですけど\nある日、運命的な出会いをして価値観が変わるんです",
      "startTime": 55.3516253225,
